{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Threat Operations Dashboard No MDE/MDI\nA single pane of glass for threat detection and response across host, identity, network, and cloud. Powered by native incident correlation, UEBA (User and Entity Behavior Analytics), ML anomalies, and Microsoft Defender Threat Intelligence (MDTI). Use the **Time Range** picker and the **tabs** below to pivot between the Overview, Host, Identity, Network, Cloud, and Sign-in Geography threat views."
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0001-0001-000000000001",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "label": "Time Range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "isGlobal": true,
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                { "durationMs": 86400000 },
                { "durationMs": 259200000 },
                { "durationMs": 604800000 },
                { "durationMs": 1209600000 },
                { "durationMs": 2592000000 },
                { "durationMs": 7776000000 }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            },
            "timeContext": { "durationMs": 2592000000 },
            "value": { "durationMs": 2592000000 }
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0001-0001-000000000002",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "selectedTab",
            "type": 1,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "value": "1"
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000001",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Threat Overview",
            "subTarget": "1",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000002",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Host Based Threats",
            "subTarget": "2",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000003",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Identity & UEBA",
            "subTarget": "3",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000004",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Network & Threat Intel",
            "subTarget": "4",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000005",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Cloud & SaaS Activity",
            "subTarget": "5",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000006",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "Sign-in Geography",
            "subTarget": "6",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "tabs"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Threat Overview",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "Whole environment threat posture in one view. Headline counts blend incidents, analytics alerts, UEBA risk, ML anomalies, and MDTI. The ATT&CK chart fuses analytic alerts with UEBA/ML anomaly tactics so leadership sees adversary behavior, not just log volume.",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "ov-info"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityIncident | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, Status) by IncidentNumber | where Status != \"Closed\" | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Open Incidents\", Sort = 1),\n  (SecurityAlert | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where AlertSeverity in (\"High\",\"Critical\") | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"High/Critical Alerts\", Sort = 2),\n  (BehaviorAnalytics | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where InvestigationPriority > 0 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"UEBA Risk Activities\", Sort = 3),\n  (Anomalies | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"ML Anomalies\", Sort = 4),\n  (ThreatIntelIndicators | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Threat Intel Indicators\", Sort = 5),\n  (AADRiskyUsers | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = dcount(UserPrincipalName) | extend Metric = \"Risky Users\", Sort = 6)\n| project Metric, Value, Sort\n| sort by Sort asc",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Threat Posture at a Glance",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Metric", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": { "palette": "blue" },
                  "numberFormat": { "unit": 17, "options": { "style": "decimal", "maximumFractionDigits": 0 } }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "name": "ov-kpis"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityIncident\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize arg_min(TimeGenerated, Severity) by IncidentNumber\n| summarize Incidents = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, {TimeRange:grain}), Severity\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Incidents Created Over Time (by Severity)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": { "createOtherGroup": 0 }
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "ov-incident-trend"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityAlert\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize Count = count() by AlertSeverity",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Alert Severity Mix",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "ov-severity-mix"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (SecurityAlert | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where isnotempty(Tactics) | extend T = split(Tactics, \",\")),\n  (Anomalies | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where isnotempty(Tactics) | extend T = split(Tactics, \";\"))\n| mv-expand Tactic = T to typeof(string)\n| extend Tactic = trim(@\"\\s+\", Tactic)\n| where isnotempty(Tactic)\n| summarize Detections = count() by Tactic\n| sort by Detections desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "MITRE ATT&CK Tactics Observed (Alerts + UEBA/ML Anomalies)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart"
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "ov-tactics"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityAlert\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize Alerts = count(), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by AlertName, ProductName, AlertSeverity\n| top 20 by Alerts desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top Detections Firing",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Alerts", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "red" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastSeen", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Alerts", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              },
              "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Alerts", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "ov-top-detections"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": { "parameterName": "selectedTab", "comparison": "isEqualTo", "value": "1" },
      "name": "group-overview"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Host Based Threats",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "Endpoint and server threat activity from Windows Security events and Linux Syslog. Lead indicators: failed logon spikes (brute force / password spray), privileged logons (4672), and anomalous process creation (4688). The Security Sensitive Events panel surfaces classic attacker tradecraft such as account creation, privileged group membership changes, audit log clearing, scheduled task and service installation, mapping directly to MITRE ATT&CK persistence, privilege escalation, and defense evasion techniques. Microsoft Defender for Endpoint (MDE) enriches every host pivot here once onboarded.",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "host-info"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (Heartbeat | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = dcount(Computer) | extend Metric = \"Hosts Reporting\", Sort = 1),\n  (SecurityEvent | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where EventID == 4625 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Failed Logons (4625)\", Sort = 2),\n  (SecurityEvent | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where EventID == 4672 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Privileged Logons (4672)\", Sort = 3),\n  (SecurityEvent | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where EventID == 4688 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Process Creations (4688)\", Sort = 4),\n  (Syslog | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where SeverityLevel in (\"err\",\"crit\",\"alert\",\"emerg\") | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Linux Critical Syslog\", Sort = 5)\n| project Metric, Value, Sort\n| sort by Sort asc",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Host Activity Snapshot",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Metric", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": { "palette": "green" },
                  "numberFormat": { "unit": 17, "options": { "style": "decimal", "maximumFractionDigits": 0 } }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "name": "host-kpis"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID == 4625\n| summarize Failures = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, {TimeRange:grain})\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Failed Logon Trend (4625) Brute Force / Spray Signal",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "linechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "host-failed-trend"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "Syslog\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize Events = count() by SeverityLevel\n| sort by Events desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Linux Syslog by Severity",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "host-syslog-sev"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID == 4625\n| summarize Failures = count(), TargetedAccounts = dcount(TargetAccount) by Computer\n| top 15 by Failures desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top Hosts by Failed Logon",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Failures", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "red" } }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Failures", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "host-top-hosts"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID == 4625\n| summarize Failures = count(), Hosts = dcount(Computer), SourceIPs = dcount(IpAddress), LogonTypes = make_set(LogonType, 10), TopSourceIP = arg_max(TimeGenerated, IpAddress).IpAddress, FirstSeen = min(TimeGenerated), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by TargetAccount\n| top 15 by Failures desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top Targeted Accounts",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Failures", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "orange" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "SourceIPs", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "red" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "FirstSeen", "formatter": 6 },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastSeen", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Failures", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "host-top-accounts"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID == 4688\n| extend Proc = tolower(tostring(split(NewProcessName, \"\\\\\")[-1]))\n| extend Parent = tolower(tostring(split(ParentProcessName, \"\\\\\")[-1]))\n| where isnotempty(Proc)\n| summarize Executions = count(), Hosts = dcount(Computer), Accounts = dcount(SubjectUserName), ParentProcesses = dcount(Parent), TopParent = arg_max(TimeGenerated, Parent).Parent, FirstSeen = min(TimeGenerated), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by Proc\n| top 25 by Executions desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Process Creation Inventory (4688) Hunt for the Unusual",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Executions", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "blue" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "Hosts", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "green" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "FirstSeen", "formatter": 6 },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastSeen", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 5000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Executions", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "host-processes"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID in (4720, 4722, 4724, 4726, 4738, 4728, 4732, 4756, 4740, 1102, 4719, 4698, 4697, 7045)\n| extend Activity = case(\n    EventID == 4720, \"Account Created\",\n    EventID == 4722, \"Account Enabled\",\n    EventID == 4724, \"Password Reset Attempt\",\n    EventID == 4726, \"Account Deleted\",\n    EventID == 4738, \"Account Changed\",\n    EventID == 4728, \"Added to Global Security Group\",\n    EventID == 4732, \"Added to Local Security Group\",\n    EventID == 4756, \"Added to Universal Security Group\",\n    EventID == 4740, \"Account Lockout\",\n    EventID == 1102, \"Audit Log Cleared\",\n    EventID == 4719, \"Audit Policy Changed\",\n    EventID == 4698, \"Scheduled Task Created\",\n    EventID == 4697, \"Service Installed\",\n    EventID == 7045, \"Service Installed (SCM)\",\n    strcat(\"Event \", tostring(EventID)))\n| summarize Count = count(), Hosts = dcount(Computer), Accounts = dcount(SubjectUserName), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by Activity, EventID\n| sort by Count desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Security Sensitive Events Persistence, PrivEsc and Defense Evasion",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "Count", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "red" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "EventID", "formatter": 1 },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastSeen", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 5000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "Count", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "host-sensitive-events"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": { "parameterName": "selectedTab", "comparison": "isEqualTo", "value": "2" },
      "name": "group-host"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "title": "Identity & UEBA",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "Identity is the new perimeter. This view leads with Sentinel UEBA: the InvestigationPriority score ranks users by anomalous behavior, fused with Entra ID Identity Protection risk and sign in telemetry across interactive, non interactive, and service principal flows.",
              "style": "info"
            },
            "name": "id-info"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "union isfuzzy=true\n  (AADRiskyUsers | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = dcount(UserPrincipalName) | extend Metric = \"Risky Users\", Sort = 1),\n  (AADUserRiskEvents | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Risk Detections\", Sort = 2),\n  (BehaviorAnalytics | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where InvestigationPriority > 0 | summarize Value = dcount(UserPrincipalName) | extend Metric = \"UEBA Flagged Users\", Sort = 3),\n  (SigninLogs | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where ResultType != 0 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Failed Sign ins\", Sort = 4),\n  (AADServicePrincipalSignInLogs | where TimeGenerated {TimeRange} | where ResultType != 0 | summarize Value = count() | extend Metric = \"Failed SP Sign ins\", Sort = 5)\n| project Metric, Value, Sort\n| sort by Sort asc",
              "size": 3,
              "title": "Identity Risk Snapshot",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Metric", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Value",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": { "palette": "purple" },
                  "numberFormat": { "unit": 17, "options": { "style": "decimal", "maximumFractionDigits": 0 } }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "name": "id-kpis"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "BehaviorAnalytics\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where InvestigationPriority > 0\n| where isnotempty(UserPrincipalName)\n| summarize PriorityScore = sum(InvestigationPriority), Activities = count(), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by UserPrincipalName\n| top 25 by PriorityScore desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "UEBA Users by Investigation Priority",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  { "columnMatch": "PriorityScore", "formatter": 8, "formatOptions": { "palette": "red" } },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastSeen", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "PriorityScore", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              },
              "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "PriorityScore", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "id-ueba-leaderboard"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "BehaviorAnalytics\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where InvestigationPriority > 0\n| summarize Count = count() by ActivityType\n| where isnotempty(ActivityType)\n| sort by Count desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "UEBA Anomalous Activity Types",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart"
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "id-ueba-activity"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "AADUserRiskEvents\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize Count = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, {TimeRange:grain}), RiskEventType\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Identity Protection Risk Detections Over Time",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart"
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "id-risk-trend"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SigninLogs\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where ResultType != 0\n| summarize Count = count() by ResultDescription\n| where isnotempty(ResultDescription)\n| top 10 by Count desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top Sign in Failure Reasons",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart"
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "id-fail-reasons"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "AADRiskyUsers\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, RiskLevel, RiskState, RiskDetail) by UserPrincipalName\n| project UserPrincipalName, RiskLevel, RiskState, RiskDetail, LastUpdated = TimeGenerated\n| order by LastUpdated desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Risky Users Current State",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RiskLevel",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "high", "representation": "failed", "text": "{0}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "medium", "representation": "4", "text": "{0}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "representation": "info", "text": "{0}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  { "columnMatch": "LastUpdated", "formatter": 6 }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 5000,
                "sortBy": [ { "itemKey": "LastUpdated", "sortOrder": 2 } ]
              }
            },
            "name": "id-risky-users-grid"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "### Entra ID Identity Protection\nThe full Identity Protection picture the ICAM team and CISO track: live risk detections, the risky user population by risk level, and the daily inflow of newly flagged users. Risk detection types such as Unfamiliar sign in properties, Anomalous token, Malicious IP, and Anonymous IP map directly to credential theft, token replay, and infrastructure abuse. Every row is a candidate for Conditional Access enforcement and SOC follow up.",
              "style": "upsell"
            },
            "name": "id-protection-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "AADRiskyUsers\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, RiskLevel, RiskState) by UserPrincipalName\n| where RiskState in (\"atRisk\",\"confirmedCompromised\")\n| extend RiskLevel = case(isempty(RiskLevel) or RiskLevel == \"none\", \"unspecified\", RiskLevel)\n| summarize Users = count() by RiskLevel\n| sort by Users desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Risky Users by Risk Level",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "33",
            "name": "id-risk-level-mix"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "AADRiskyUsers\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where RiskState in (\"atRisk\",\"confirmedCompromised\")\n| summarize arg_min(TimeGenerated, RiskLevel) by UserPrincipalName\n| summarize NewRiskyUsers = count() by bin(TimeGenerated, 1d)\n| order by TimeGenerated asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "New Risky Users per Day",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
